description:
Danny welcomes Bravo superfan and TV queen Leslie Grossman (American Horror Story/Popular) to talk all things Bravo. They cover #RHONY, #RHOP, Bethenny Getting Married, and so much more. Plus, Daniel Levy (Schitt's Creek) calls in for a quick pop culture chat.

*For bonus episodes, join the Patreon at www.Patreon.com/EverythingIconic Web: www.EverythingIconic.com Twitter: www.Twitter.com/DannyPellegrino Instagram: www.Instagram.com/DannyPellegrino
